1027.name: AA CuAl14Fe
1027.Applications: Cladding components undergoing metal to metal wear with high friction and or heavy surface loads on top of cast iron, steels and or bronzes.
1027.Suitable_For: Deep drawing dies for stainless steel, aluminium, magnesium and titanium parts. Sleeves, spindles, cable winches guides, gliding surfaces, pulling equipment. (usualy preheating 300°C prior to welding is recomended to reduce cracks)
